# Turing machine to recognize the following language:
#  L = {w | w is palindrome}
# White is represented as .
q0 q1 q2              # States
a b                   # String alphabet
a b .                 # Tape alphabet
q0                    # Initial state
q1                    # Accepting states
2                     # Number of tapes
q0 q0 a R a . R a     # Transitions. The last three character have to be repeated for each tape
q0 q0 b R b . R b
q0 q1 . L . . L .
q1 q1 a L a a S a
q1 q1 b L b b S b
q1 q1 a L a b S b
q1 q1 b L b a S a
q1 q2 . R . a S a
q1 q2 . R . b S b
q2 q2 a R a a L a
q2 q2 b R b b L b
q2 q1 . S . . S .